&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Sr. Director of Marketing, Consulting Business, we’re looking for a curious, organized, and execution-focused Digital Marketing Coordinator to join Reach3 Insights. In this role, you’ll support day-to-day marketing programs that drive awareness, engagement, and pipeline for Reach3 Insights and Angus Reid, working with smart, kind people who love turning ideas into clear campaigns, useful content, and stronger client connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is open to candidates based in Vancouver, BC, with a hybrid working model of 2 to 3 days per week in office designed to support connection, focused work, and real life outside of work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;About Reach3 Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
