&lt;p&gt;As part of Rival Group — alongside Rival Technologies and Angus Reid — we&#39;re helping transform the insights industry through AI-accelerated, messaging-based conversational insights. Our work reaches consumers and business audiences in ways that feel fresh, human, and genuinely useful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you&#39;ll help strengthen the digital presence of our consulting and advisory businesses by keeping our websites, campaigns, social channels, and event marketing organized, polished, and moving forward.&lt;/p&gt;
