&lt;li&gt;Support landing page and product page creation, updates, and ongoing optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and implement improvements to content quality, structure, accuracy, and user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help maintain consistency across web properties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Social media management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and schedule engaging content across social channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal stakeholders to source, create, and publish content, including thought leadership, reports, announcements, and event promotion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor engagement and support basic performance tracking so the team can understand what is resonating.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help maintain a consistent, polished, and on-brand social presence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Campaign management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up and execute marketing campaigns in Salesforce, including campaign tracking, member management, and reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and deploy email campaigns and newsletters through HubSpot or similar tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage campaign lists, segmentation, and data hygiene.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure campaigns are launched accurately, on schedule, and with the right follow-through.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Events and webinar support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support webinars, virtual events, and occasional in-person events from planning through follow-up.&lt;/li&gt;
